        <div type="letter">
        <opener><dateline><date when=""><!--Write the date here --><dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe"><!--person name --></persName>:</salute>
        </opener>
            <p>Postal just received. Sentence to be left out on page four of my manuscript. Again the Jew for never has the race been famed for martial ardour on the cold fields of actual man-made fighting. The rest of the paragraph to stand exactly as it is. Please be sure that this sentence is left out.</p>
           <p>Will wire again on receipt of proof.</p>
           <closure><persName key="amy_lowell">Amy Lowell</persName></closure>
            
